      "commitHash": "92ac5510391900b693c9baba3c0938508e22da7d",
      "commitMessage": "FirebaseAuthGuard: hard timeouts to prevent multi-minute hangs\n\nProduction logs showed every authenticated request hanging for 5-7 minutes when outbound fetch from the API host to Firebase or Supabase REST returned 'TypeError: fetch failed' (transient Railway network/socket issues). Each hung request held an HTTP socket and starved the public /api/radio/current endpoint. Add explicit Promise.race timeouts: verifyIdToken 6s, users lookup 5s, ensureUserProfile 5s and run in background. Auth now fast-fails instead of stalling the whole API.",
