    "id": "8d1f05a1-ddae-459f-ab06-99857ff81b7f",
    "status": "REMOVED",
    "createdAt": "2026-04-19T20:05:49.112Z",
    "meta": {
      "branch": "main",
      "buildOnly": false,
      "commitAuthor": "Tmaku18",
      "commitHash": "84045be1916320d1e31b071fd64dd2ceede31b93",
      "commitMessage": "Radio + admin login resilience under DB pressure\n\n- Cache last-known radio track for 60min (was 5min) and serve TTL-less snapshot when DB times out so listeners aren't kicked to 'no_content' during Supabase outages. - Cache getAllFreeRotationSongs in memory for 30s and reduce free-rotation refill loop from 50 attempts to 8 to stop hammering Postgres when stacks are empty. - Background rotation tick now skips stations whose snapshot is <90s old and spreads station refreshes by 250ms to avoid bursting 24+ queries at once. - isAdminUser checks ADMIN_EMAILS allowlist first and 4s-timeouts the role lookup so admin login doesn't hang when /users/me/check-admin is slow.",
